{"tid":389203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★懲罰毒撚！日本近日傳出要「徵收單身稅」。","createTime":"2017-09-06T04:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T09:12:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c17eebf4a4a70cb0000a2b3caeba01bb9caa03e","tid":389203,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"據日文版《赫芬頓郵報》報導，《北國新聞》刊登了這則「單身稅」報導後，引起了日本網友的熱烈討論。有部分網友憤怒地表示，「這是逼人民在結婚和稅務負擔上做選擇」、「我根本不想結婚」、「單親婦女怎麼辦？」、「這對同性戀者很不禮貌！」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，其實國外早有「單身稅」先例。由於少子化的關係，位在東歐的保加利亞在1968年頒布「單身稅」，對25-29歲的單身者，徵收收入的5%；30-49歲單身者則徵收收入10%。但保加利亞這項政策並沒有提高生育率，因為當時蘇聯經濟不穩定的關係，導致生育率持續低迷。直到1989年的「東歐劇變」之後，保加利亞迎來了政權的轉換，也使「單身稅」跟著被廢除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170905/1004447.htm?t=日本擬課「單身稅」？　網友暴怒：同性戀者怎麼辦！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170905%2F1004447.htm%3Ft%3D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%AC%E8%AA%B2%E3%80%8C%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E7%A8%85%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E6%9A%B4%E6%80%92%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E8%80%85%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E8%BE%A6%EF%BC%81&d=7hiTfe62AKfRJLUG5Et5QzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=bed5c0e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170905/1004447.htm?t=日本擬課「單身稅」？　網友暴怒：同性戀者怎麼辦！</a>"},{"pid":"3bbeabf4c01219f9bfb4860194fa0247c7be64c2","tid":389203,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2776/d2776258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2776%2Fd2776258.jpg&h=bdb774de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"018ad6978099fce465292ed2b8f5dc0e609e5f62","tid":389203,"uid":139272,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"如果有，連登起碼一半人都要交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都要"},{"pid":"2b3e8a88ff055f0b2d04e9b7d8fda8ba767e9030","tid":389203,"uid":33848,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"cite